    "description": "月光？<strong>无聊的</strong>！ 你会做饭<strong>摩莱士 </strong>！ 在你的花园里种植原料，制作月光并用主要原料升级它 - 一种讨厌的 <strong>痣</strong> 想吃掉你的庄稼！<br><br>你有一个废弃的废墟农场，它经常被想要吃掉你庄稼的顽固鼹鼠袭击！ 清理瓦砾，修复你的花园并种植不同的作物来制作最不寻常的月光！ 不要忘记害虫防治，亲手保卫你的庄稼，或者建立一个坚固的防御系统！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用您必须发现的独特食谱，完成制作月光的整个过程</li><li>农场生活管理、维修、升级和播种</li><li>保护你的农场免受鼹鼠攻击你自己或在各种防御手段的帮助下</li><li>出售成品并将收益用于农场</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不要忘记：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.poster.avif?t=1764358710\" width=604 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.webm?t=1764358710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/133db20a5221b506865c2a6aa7d46d9e.mp4?t=1764358710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/906a33c7beacfa0d3bfddbe8c52561d9.poster.avif?t=1764358710\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/906a33c7beacfa0d3bfddbe8c52561d9.webm?t=1764358710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293400/extras/906a33c7beacfa0d3bfddbe8c52561d9.mp4?t=1764358710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
